Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:35.39,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:43.42,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:51.61,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:57.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:02:02.50,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,projecting myself a little exaggeratedly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:07.88,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:13.21,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:19.81,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:27.84,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:39.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:46.59,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:54.62,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,before it all becomes a thing of the past
