Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:38.52,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sketched by Oreki Hotaro"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.95,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:08.71,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:12.71,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:18.08,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our snooze-time date
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.30,0:24:38.30,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat of your budding warmth troubles me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:49.02,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how I feel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.44,0:24:55.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.95,0:25:01.34,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:07.06,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.09,0:25:12.06,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:15.02,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:18.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.81,0:25:22.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
